{"tid":1628574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講 撚 咗 核 爆 都 唔 割 ","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:52:28.000Z","uid":181719,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb4e93e495babc9d17a2f41e9b221f5ea796b97","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:25.000Z","msg":"裝修又有人嘈<br />\n<br />\n獅鳥又有人嘈<br />\n<br />\n集港島定分區攪都有人嘈<br />\n<br />\n係咪話討論就等於割呢？<br />\n當然唔係，但希望大家知道，好多時討論都係講吓講吓就反面。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有段時間，泛民討論過自己「有沒有不分裂的本錢」，如果大家有追開政治野，應該記得。<br />\n<br />\n幾年落黎嘅局勢話我地知個答案。<br />\n人地有資源有後台，分裂咗都只係輸，唔會死。<br />\n<br />\n但我地分裂咗，輸咗，就死撚梗。<br />\n<br />\n點樣攪，攪唔攪，大家可以各自努力，自行參與<br />\n<br />\n最重要係記得核爆都唔撚割<br />\n<br />\n講過就係"},{"pid":"5013ed2b9111537558b148feedfaa906d870f44c","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6a0ea5c4ca102f0cce70e314c116229f6fe58700","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"一推推"},{"pid":"487d78ac8855dd665bc6481b96f7e126619fca57","tid":1628574,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a0034e0e75ac419a4d93252798b0ed5834ef2","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"再推推"},{"pid":"c171ffb62801231333b98e7c26fcd80d75b32a07","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"三推推"},{"pid":"1d0ab7d90c5565d34d9e5205e21d2d38f0c5b74b","tid":1628574,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487d78ac8855dd665bc6481b96f7e126619fca57","tid":1628574,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited